<!DOCTYPE html>
<% let title="Homepage" ; include!("./head.stpl"); %>

  <body>
    <% include!("./navbar.stpl"); %>
      <div class="content-container">
        <div class="content">
          <h1 class="centered-text job-count-text">Currently there are <span class="job-count">
              <%= total_jobs_count %>
            </span> rust jobs
            listed</h1>
          <table class="pure-table centered-table">
            <thead>
              <tr class="table-header">
                <th>Job Title</th>
                <th>Perm or Freelance</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Location</th>
                <th>Budget</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <% for job in jobs { %>
                <tr>
                  <td class="fira-sans">
                    <%= job.title %>
                  </td>
                  <td class="fira-sans">
                    <%= job.job_type %>
                  </td>
                  <td class="fira-sans">Full-time</td>
                  <td class="fira-sans">
                    <%= job.location %>
                  </td>
                  <td class="fira-sans">
                    <%= job.budget %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <%}%>
                  <!-- Add more rows as needed -->
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <div class="centered-link">
            <a href="#" class="normal-link">See the full list</a>
          </div>
          <div class="container">
            <div class="box">
              <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed euismod quam eu mauris laoreet, sit
                amet dictum urna feugiat.</p>
              <p>Integer scelerisque libero sit amet ligula sagittis, nec laoreet elit fermentum.</p>
              <a href="#" class="register-button">Post A Job Today As Employee</a>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
              <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed euismod quam eu mauris laoreet, sit
                amet dictum urna feugiat.</p>
              <p>Integer scelerisque libero sit amet ligula sagittis, nec laoreet elit fermentum.</p>
              <a href="#" class="register-button">Register As A Rust Developer</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-column">
          <div class="footer-column-title">Terms and policies</div>
          <a href="#">Random Term</a>
          <a href="#">Random Policy</a>
          <a href="#">Random Agreement</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-column">
          <div class="footer-column-title">Social</div>
          <a href="#">Facebook</a>
          <a href="#">Twitter</a>
          <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        </div>
      </div>
  </body>

  </html>